  "texts": [
    "The emerging field of explainable AI (XAI) brings transparency and help users understand decision making process of ML model.",
    "The effort addresses the issue of \"AI black boxes,\" or systems where core operations are opaque, keeping engineers and practitioners in the dark about results.",
    "Researchers and engineers push for openness in ML system operation, opposing such opacity.",
    "XAI aims to reveal the reasoning behind an ML's decisions by removing layers of complexity.",
    "Employing feature importances in this study will reveal role of input parameters in final predictions."
  ],
